n, s = map(int, input().split())
    participants = []
    for i in range(n):
        t, b = input().split()
        participants.append((t, int(b)))
    winners = []
    for t, b in participants:
        if b <= s:
            winners.append(t)
            s -= b
    print(len(winners))
    for t in winners:
        print(t)

n = int(input())
    a = list(map(int, input().split()))
    a.sort()
    a.reverse()
    x = 1
    for i in range(n):
        if a[i] < x:
            break
        x += 1
    p = x
    q = 1
    for i in range(n):
        if a[i] < p:
            break
        q += 1
    print(x, q)
    for i in range(p):
        for j in range(q):
            print(a[i*q+j], end=' ')
        print()

R, C = [int(x) for x in input().split()]
    letters = []
    for i in range(R):
        letters.append(input())
    letters = [list(x) for x in letters]
    letters = [list(x) for x in zip(*letters)]
    count = 0
    for i in range(C):
        if len(set(letters[i])) == 1:
            count += 1
    print(count)

    acc.sort()
    acc = acc[::-1]
    count = 0
    for i in range(N):
        if acc[i] == i+1:
            count += 1
    print(count)

n, k = [int(x) for x in input().split()]
    v = [int(x) for x in input().split()]
    v.sort()
    v = v[::-1]
    min_time = 0
    for i in range(n):
        if i % k == 0:
            min_time += 1
        min_time += v[i]
    print(min_time)

n, k = map(int, input().split())
    v = list(map(int, input().split()))
    v.sort()
    v = v[::-1]
    i = 0
    while i < n:
        if v[i] == v[i+k-1]:
            i += k
        else:
            break
    print(i//k+1)

        i += 1
    print(n - i)
